.TH CVT2PIC 9.1
.SH NAME
cvt2pic, dumppic, ega2pic, face2pic, gif2pic, jpg2pic, nasa2pic, pcx2pic, picopic, sgi2pic, targa2pic, tiff2pic, utah2pic, xbm2pic \- convert other formats to picture files
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B fb/cvt2pic
[
.I file
]
